items.name: reisen_udongein_inaba/鈴仙・優曇華院・イナバ/레이센우동게인이나바 (Touhou)
items.description:
NOTE: ALL CHARACTERS IN THE IMAGES ARE ADULTS.

How to Use This Model

USE THEM SIMULTANEOUSLY. In this case, you need to download both reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.pt and reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.safetensors, then use reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.pt as texture inversion embedding, and use reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.safetensors as LoRA at the same time.

それらを同時に使用してください。この場合、reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.ptとreisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.safetensorsの両方をダウンロード する必要があります。reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.ptをテクスチャ反転埋め込みとして使用し、同時にreisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.safetensorsをLoRAとして使用してください。

同时使用它们。在这种情况下，您需要下载reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.pt和reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.safetensors这两个文件，然后将reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.pt用作纹理反转嵌入， 同时使用reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou.safetensors作为LoRA。

(Translated with ChatGPT)

The trigger word is reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou, and the recommended tags are masterpiece, best quality, highres, solo, {reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou:1.10}, animal_ears, long_hair, rabbit_ears, purple_hair, red_eyes, very_long_hair, necktie, red_necktie, bangs, breasts, blush, smile.

How This Model Is Trained

This model is trained with HCP-Diffusion. And the auto-training framework is maintained by DeepGHS Team.

Why Some Preview Images Not Look Like Reisen Udongein Inaba Touhou

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is fine-tune the tags you use.

I Felt This Model May Be Overfitting or Underfitting, What Shall I Do

Our model has been published on huggingface repository - CyberHarem/reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou, where models of all the steps are saved. Also, we published the training dataset on huggingface dataset - CyberHarem/reisen_udongein_inaba_touhou, which may be helpful to you.

Why Not Just Using The Better-Selected Images

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention. It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

items.name: Lance Bass (2000's)
items.description:
This LoRA is based on Lance Bass during the 2000's. Think frosted blond tips and spiky and gelled hair.

In the early 2000s, Lance Bass was a prominent figure in the entertainment world as a member of the hugely successful boy band NSYNC. Known for his distinctive bass voice and boyish charm, Lance and NSYNC released hit albums like "No Strings Attached" (2000) and "Celebrity" (2001), with chart-topping singles such as "Bye Bye Bye" and "It's Gonna Be Me."

Beyond music, Lance Bass ventured into acting with appearances on TV shows like "7th Heaven" and became a pop culture icon. His public coming out as gay in 2006 made him a notable LGBTQ+ advocate, and he also engaged in philanthropic efforts and business ventures during this period, leaving a lasting mark on the early 2000s entertainment landscape.

Weights between .8 and 1 work well.

items.name: EYE SEE YOU
items.description:
English/中文

Is that an eye? It gazes at me through the hole in the wall, and as I look deeper, the eye blinks and disappears into the darkness. There's still something looking at me, and when I turn my head, I see those eyes. The pictures on the wall, the books on the shelf, the vase on the table, all sprout eyes. Black, red, blue, they silently stare at me, conveying some mysterious message.

I cannot believe what I am seeing, and crazy thoughts fill my mind. I close my eyes, hoping that this eerie sight will vanish. But when I open my eyes again, the number of eyes has increased, and their gaze has become more intense.

Fear drives me to flee the apartment. I see that giant eye! It hangs among the clouds, emitting a terrifying aura. The pupil of that eye is unfathomably deep, as if it can devour everything. It silently stares at me, revealing an indescribable power in its gaze.

Suddenly, the giant eye slowly closes. Before its eyelids completely shut, everything around me gradually disappears.

The eye is now completely closed.

This LoRA takes inspiration from gaze and can add eyes to any object or even the sky, creating highly artistic and surreal images.

Instructions:

  • Recommended trigger words: (objects) with (color) ceyes

  • Weight: 0.7-1

  • Positive prompt words: realistic, no human,

  • Negative prompt words: easynegative, painting, human, man, woman, girl, boy, manuscript,

  • Recommended models: cyberrealistic_v31 (This LoRA is based on training with SD1.5, so it can be applied to most checkpoints based on SD1.5. Different checkpoints may produce slightly different results.)

  • Example image generation parameters: Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras, CFG scale: 7, Size: 512x768, Denoising strength: 0.5, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+. (Hires upscaler effect is not necessary but still produces good results)

Creating this LoRA has taken a lot of effort, and I hope to receive more comments and feedback, as well as images created using this model. If you have any questions or suggestions regarding this LoRA, please feel free to contact me. I look forward to your feedback!

那是一只眼睛吗？墙壁的裂缝中它注视着我，我向深处看去，那只眼睛眨了一下，消失在黑暗中。还有东西在看我，当我转过头时，我看到了那些眼睛，墙壁上的照片、书架上的书、桌子上的花瓶，都长出了眼睛。黑色的、红色的、蓝色的，它们静静地凝视着我，在传递某种神秘的信息。

我无法相信眼前的景象，脑海中涌现出疯狂的念头。我闭上眼睛，希望这诡异的景象能够消失。但当我再次睁开双眼，眼睛的数量却越来越多，它们的注视也变得更加强烈。

恐惧驱使我逃离公寓。我看到了那个巨大的眼睛！它悬挂在浓云之间，散发着无比恐怖的气息。那眼睛的瞳孔深邃无比，仿佛能够吞噬一切。它无声地凝视着我，目光中透露出一种无法言喻的力量。

突然，那只巨大的眼睛缓缓闭合。在它的眼皮完全合拢之前，周围一切的存在都在渐渐消失。

眼睛已经完全闭上了。

此LoRA以注视为灵感，可以在任何物体甚至天空中添加眼睛，可用于生成非常具有艺术感的超现实图像。

生成建议：

  • 推荐触发词：事物 with 颜色 ceyes

  • 权重：0.7-1

  • 正面提示词：realistic, no human,

  • 负面提示词：easynegative, painting, human, man, woman, girl, boy, manuscript,

  • 推荐模型：cyberrealistic_v31 (该LoRA以SD1.5为底模训练，故可适用于大多数以SD1.5为基础的大模型，不同模型产生的效果会有少许差异。)

  • 例图生成参数：Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras, CFG scale: 7, Size: 512x768, Denoising strength: 0.5, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+,（不使用Hires效果也很好）

这个LoRA制作花费了我很多精力，希望大家能多多评论和返图T-T。如果你对该LoRA有任何疑问或者建议，随时都可以联系我。期待你的反馈！
